61
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:39,080
Malam ini, ada Nona Su
yang menemani.

62
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:40,840
Aku tiba-tiba jadi merasa…

63
00:05:42,039 --> 00:05:43,479
…sedikit terharu.

64
