198
00:15:47,679 --> 00:15:48,999
Menggoda Su Yuela?

199
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:50,840
Aku mana mampu melakukannya?

200
00:15:51,319 --> 00:15:52,239
Jangan panik dulu.

201
00:15:52,359 --> 00:15:54,480
